","in stock",new,"12500.00 BDT",http://127.0.0.1:8003/product/ax44-stream-ax1800-wifi-6-router,http://127.0.0.1:8000/media/634bab421ce4e.png,unknown

column4: >The NETGEAR Nighthawk AX4 4-Stream AX3000 WiFi Router supports the latest generation WiFi 6 technology to provide greater network capacity with the consistent and powerful signal strength to all your connected devices. The Nighthawk AX4 WiFi router delivers a new level of Gigabit WiFi connectivity so you can connect, stream, and download faster to newer mobile devices. A powerful dual-core processor with a fully offloaded CPU increases the overall performance of the network. OFDMA, 1024 QAM, and 160MHz channel support vastly improve network efficiency to deliver 4 times the performance as compared to previous WiFi standards. Enjoy smoother streaming, faster downloads, and improved gaming and video conferencing. More WiFi streams mean more available bandwidth and less congestion for all the devices in the WiFi network. The Nighthawk AX4 provides consistent and powerful signal strength to multiple devices at the same time so you can enjoy smooth gaming and 4K UHD video streaming, faster file transfers, and backups. Now maximize the wireless benefits of your Gigabit internet service plans so you can connect, stream, and download faster. The latest Wi-Fi 6 standard supports 160MHz bandwidth that enables Gigabit Wi-Fi speeds to newer PCs and mobile devices that support 160MHz bandwidth. Futureproof your purchase to keep pace as you add the latest devices to your home Wi-Fi. Orthogonal Frequency-Division Multiple Access (OFDMA) enables efficient data scheduling so that more transmissions can be sent at the same time, resulting in an impressive capacity increase in your network. This increased or available bandwidth allows you to add more devices to your network. Nighthawk AX4 supports uplink and downlink OFDMA to efficiently use air-time with better frequency reuse, reduced latency, and increased network efficiency. This is extremely useful for latency-sensitive applications such as virtual reality (VR), augmented reality (AR), and Internet of things (IoT) sensors. Nighthawk AX4's powerful dual-core processor with a fully offloaded CPU is designed to transfer multi-gigs of data. Full-packet processing offload means zero loads on the CPU, so you can do more on your WiFi without slowing down. Enjoy smoother Ultra-HD 4K video streaming and gaming without interruptions. It has 3 years of warranty

column17: >. Featuring 802.11ax Wi-Fi support, this router is designed to efficiently communicate with multiple devices simultaneously to deliver wireless speeds of up to 5.4 Gb/s over the 2.4 GHz and 5 GHz frequencies. You can quickly configure and manage the high-performance router using the Nighthawk mobile app, including setting up guest network logins for added security. You can also issue voice commands using Amazon Alexa and Google Assistant. Four Gigabit Ethernet LAN ports are available for connecting wired devices such as computers, smart TVs, and video game consoles. Plugging a flash drive into the integrated USB 3.1 Gen 1 port allows you to share files and media with all connected devices across the network. The Nighthawk AX6 also includes a free 1-year subscription to Netgear Armor, which provides a suite of tools to protect your network's connected devices from a variety of threats.
